{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "d21fc1dc-29dc-454f-b89e-a73ae7582d09", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d21fc1dc-29dc-454f-b89e-a73ae7582d09@2.pkg/1772597510214/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597511239", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d21fc1dc-29dc-454f-b89e-a73ae7582d09@2.pkg/1772597510214/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597511239"}, "identifier": "d21fc1dc-29dc-454f-b89e-a73ae7582d09", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<ol>\n</ol>\n\n<p>A（正确）：数据体现国有经济在关键领域和前沿科技的主导作用；</p>\n\n<p>B（片面）：虽表述正确，但未直接反映题干中\"主导作用\"的核心信息；</p>\n\n<p>C（错误）：国有经济主要在重要行业和关键领域发挥主导作用，并非\"全面主导\"；</p>\n\n<p>D（错误）：国有经济服务于全体人民根本利益。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<ol>\n\t<li>（原创）2025年，国务院国资委发布数据显示，国有资本在能源、通信等关键领域占比超80%，在人工智能、量子科技等前沿领域投资同比增长35%。同时，国有企业牵头组建16个国家级创新联合体，突破多项\"卡脖子\"技术。这表明（　　）</li>\n</ol>\n", "title": "（原创）2025年，国务院国资委发布数据显示，国有资本在能源、通信等关键领域占比超80%，在人工智能、量子科技等前沿领域投资同比增长35%。同时，国有企业牵头组建16个国家级创新联合体，突破多项\"卡脖子\"技术。这表明（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/d21fc1dc-29dc-454f-b89e-a73ae7582d09@2.pkg/item.json?v=1754580329898", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "ori